  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to Pixman</title>

    <para>
      The <application>Pixman</application> package contains a library that
      provides low-level pixel manipulation features such as image
      compositing and trapezoid rasterization.
    </para>

    &lfs121_checked;

